e="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> Under this approach the suppliers cannot apply wildly varying levies on to the customer.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> The positive is that we retain the target based obligation but with a cost ceiling.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p></div></body></html>